  metaDescription: "Income Tax Act (Canada) s12(12) + s12(13) deems profit on residential property held under 365 days to be business income — not a capital gain. 100% inclusion (vs 50%/66.67%). No principal residence exemption. Narrow life-event exceptions. Effective 1 Jan 2023. Confirmed April 2026.",
